      "text": [
        " : \"قَضَى رَسُولُ اَللَّهِ صَلَّى اَللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَ آلِهِ أَنْ يُقَدَّمَ صَاحِبُ اَلْيَمِينِ فِي اَلْمَجْلِسِ بِالْكَلاَمِ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3240 - Muhammad ibn Muslim narrated from Abu Jafar Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as) who said:\n\"The Messenger of Allah (swt) (peace be upon him and his family) ruled that the one on the right should speak first in a gathering.\""
